sis</a></div></div><div class="illustrated-product"><div class="illu" style="width:45%;"><img data-opt-src="https://mlyoasgpptk8.i.optimole.com/zVggxes-2IMZSFQw/w:220/h:308/q:auto/https://www.iris-france.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/10/QUADRI-LA-GUERRE.jpg"  width="220" height="308" src="https://mlyoasgpptk8.i.optimole.com/zVggxes-2IMZSFQw/w:220/h:308/q:eco/https://www.iris-france.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/10/QUADRI-LA-GUERRE.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt=""><noscript><img width="220" height="308" src="https://mlyoasgpptk8.i.optimole.com/zVggxes-2IMZSFQw/w:220/h:308/q:auto/https://www.iris-france.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/10/QUADRI-LA-GUERRE.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt=""></noscript></div> <a href="/publications/la-guerre/" class="article-title" style="width:48%;float:left;">La guerre</a><div class="author"><span class="with">Par</span> <a class="qtip-people" data-info-qtip="Directeur de recherche à l'IRIS" href="https://www.iris-france.org/chercheurs/barthelemy-courmont">Barthélémy Courmont</a></div></div><div class="illustrated-product"><div class="illu" style="width:45%;"><img data-opt-src="https://mlyoasgpptk8.i.optimole.com/zVggxes-Ssx6_bB6/w:220/h:308/q:auto/https://www.iris-france.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/QUADRI-50-IDEES.jpg"  width="220" height="308" src="https://mlyoasgpptk8.i.optimole.com/zVggxes-Ssx6_bB6/w:220/h:308/q:eco/https://www.iris-france.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/QUADRI-50-IDEES.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt=""><noscript><img width="220" height="308" src="https://mlyoasgpptk8.i.optimole.com/zVggxes-Ssx6_bB6/w:220/h:308/q:auto/https://www.iris-france.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/07/QUADRI-50-IDEES.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt=""></noscript></div> <a href="/publications/50-idees-recues-sur-letat-du-monde-4/" class="article-title" style="width:48%;fl