low"><div class="title">Nous suivre</div><div class="social-footer clearfix"><div class="social-block social-footer-icon"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/InstitutIRIS" target="_blank" class="fb-header">&nbsp;</a></div><div class="social-block social-footer-icon"><a href="https://twitter.com/InstitutIRIS"  target="_blank" class="tw-header">&nbsp;</a></div><div class="social-block social-footer-icon"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/iris---institut-de-relations-internationales-et-strat-giques" target="_blank" class="in-header">&nbsp;</a></div><div class="social-block social-footer-icon"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/institutiris" target="_blank" class="yt-header">&nbsp;</a></div><div class="social-block social-footer-icon"><a href="https://www.iris-france.org/feed/" target="_blank" class="rss-header">&nbsp;</a></div></div><div class="newsletter-footer"><div class="label">S’inscrire à la newsletter</div><div id="ninja_forms_form_5_cont" class="ninja-forms-cont"><div id="ninja_forms_form_5_wrap" class="ninja-forms-form-wrap"><div id="ninja_forms_form_5_response_msg" style="" class="ninja-forms-response-msg "></div><form id="ninja_forms_form_5" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post" name="" action="https://www.iris-france.org/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php?action=ninja_forms_ajax_submit" class="ninja-forms-form"><input type="hidden" id="_wpnonce" name="_wpnonce" value="878941dee5" /><input type="hidden" name="_wp_http_referer" value="/publications/geopolitique-de-letat-islamique/" /> <input type="hidden" name="_ninja_forms_display_submit" value="1"> <input type="hidden" name="_form_id"  id="_form_id" value="5"><div class="hp-wrap"> <label>Si vous êtes un être humain et que vous voyez ce champ, merci de le laisser vide. <input type="text" value="" name="_hQj03"> <input type="hidden" value="_hQj03" name="_hp_name"> </label></div><div id="ninja_forms_form_5_all_fields_wrap" class="ninja-forms-all-fields-wrap"><div class="ninja-forms-required-items">Les cham